      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pine_Castle%2C_Florida"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The Pine Castle Historical Society, born from a 2011 women’s club mural, now preserves the town’s rural heritage.",
